  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764924754\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764924754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764924754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/a46c796b3d27d029feaee0e4ea2c857d.avif?t=1764924754\" width=610 height=210 /></span><br>Features of the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Diego is a very fast and accurate shooter.<br></li><li>Diego is armed and can fight back against the rebellious plants.<br></li><li>Diego can move from island to island via teleport.<br></li><li>Diego is ready to shoot all the dangerous bushes with tomatoes.<br></li><li>Diego is afraid of flying saws, but the bullet is able to stop and redirect the saw.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/eed5cab60c1384fee6ca91823253bcee.poster.avif?t=1764924754\" width=594 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/eed5cab60c1384fee6ca91823253bcee.webm?t=1764924754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564980/extras/eed5cab60c1384fee6ca91823253bcee.mp4?t=1764924754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >History:</h2>Diego is a Mexican farmer who is fond of growing tomatoes. Diego accidentally bought a fertilizer with radioactive elements and now the tomatoes are ready to fight back against Diego they no longer want in the jar.",
